texmf.cnf:
parse_first_line.tex = t
shell_escape.lhplain = f

tex -ini -jobname tex lhplain.ini >/dev/null # override tex.fmt to use A4 paper
tex -ini -enc lhplain.ini >/dev/null # use %&lhplain on first line of .tex file


  The road to wisdom? Well, it's plain
  And simple to express:
  Err
  and err
  and err again,
  but less
  and less
  and less.
